</title>
<servinfosub id = "S6JB0A6306005001">
<title>
Inspection
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that belt is free from any damage and properly fitted in pulley groove.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check belt tension by measuring how much it deflects when pushed at intermediate point between pulleys with about 10 kg (22 lb) force.
</ptxt>
