<title>
Adjustment
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
To adjust P&#x002F;S belt tension, loosen tension pulley bolt (2) and nut (1) and turn tension pulley (3) using hexagon wrench (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Adjust belt tension to specification, and then tighten tension pulley bolt (2) and nut (1) to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T6C001">
<t-part>
P&#x002F;S belt tension pulley bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
